data.description: Rental investment opportunity!! This newer duplex is one of few in the valley. 2008 built. Corner lot situated in a convenient location for shopping and schools. Each side is a 3 bed 1.5 bath. The kitchen/dining room areas are large for a rental. Tons of cabinetry storage. Side #A has been completely renovated with modern updates. Comes with the storage shed on the North side. Side #B has a fenced yard with a large storage shed and beautiful gazebo. Both sides are in great condition. Both come with all appliances including washers and dryers. Laundry is upstairs on both units. All bedrooms are of good size and all bedrooms and full bathrooms are on the upper level. Multiple paved parking spaces indicated. Projected monthly income $3000-$3600
